<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    {{> meta}}
    {{> head}}
    <style>
        #c4kheader {
            background-image: url("../assets/images/cb/cover/c4k_cover.jpg");
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: bottom;
            background-size: cover;

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="scroll-assist">
{{> navbar}}
<div class="main-container">
    <section class="page-title page-title-1 bg-dark" id="c4kheader">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="mb0 bold uppercase">CODE4KIDS</h2>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <ol class="breadcrumb breadcrumb-2">
            <li>
                <a href="#web-track" target="_self">Intro</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#syllabus">Elements</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#faqs">FAQ</a>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </section>
    <a name="web-track"></a>
    <section class="bg-white">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <!-- Title -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
                    <h1 class="thin">Web Design Track</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Description -->
            <div class="row mb-xs-0">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
                    <p class="lead">
                        Computer programming is the most important skill of the twenty first century, and the earlier a
                        kid starts, the better he will get. Coding Blocks brings to you Code4Kids, a one of its kind
                        computer programming course for school kids. Through this course, your child will get an insight
                        into the beautiful world of computer programming, as well as learn the basics of web
                        development. This is the ideal course to enrol your child into, as it will cover all basic
                        concepts that a child need to strengthen. The course will be taught by industry experts from
                        colleges like IIT-Delhi, IIIT-Delhi, DTU and many more.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-dark">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <a name="syllabus"></a>
            <!-- Sub items-->
            <div class="row mt40 pt20">
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-xs-24">
                    <i class="icon mb32 ti ti-game"></i>
                    <h6 class="uppercase">SCRATCH</h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Brick Blast</li>
                        <li>Question War</li>
                        <li>Raining Stars</li>
                        <li>Maze Craze</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-xs-24">
                    <i class="icon mb32 ti ti-file"></i>
                    <h6 class="uppercase">HTML</h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Tags</li>
                        <li>Links</li>
                        <li>Tables</li>
                        <li>Lists</li>
                        <li>Forms</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-xs-24">
                    <i class="icon mb32 ti ti-write"></i>
                    <h6 class="uppercase">CSS</h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Animated Buttons</li>
                        <li>Alert Buttons</li>
                        <li>Progress Bar</li>
                        <li>Tooltip</li>
                        <li>Image Overlay Hover</li>
                        <li>Image Effects</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-xs-24">
                    <i class="icon mb32 fa fa-file-code-o"></i>
                    <h6 class="uppercase">JavaScript</h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Variables</li>
                        <li>Function</li>
                        <li>Parameters</li>
                        <li>Scope</li>
                        <li>Operators</li>
                        <li>Conditions</li>
                        <li>Loops</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <p>Apart from this, students will also create some applications during the course, based on the basic
                    concepts they learn. Some examples of these are To-Do List, Calculator and Signup Form.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <a name="faqs"></a>
    <section class="bg-secondary">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
                    <h4 class="mb16">FAQ</h4>
                    <p class="lead mb64">(Drop a line at admissions@codingblocks.com if you have further queries)</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
                    <ul class="accordion accordion-2 one-open">
                        <li>
                            <div class="title">
                                <h4 class="inline-block mb0">
                                    Who should do this course?
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    School kids from classes VI-X looking to start computer programming.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="title">
                                <h4 class="inline-block mb0">
                                    Will this course help if my child wants a career in technology?
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    Yes, it certainly will help as computer programming is the most basic skill
                                    required.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="title">
                                <h4 class="inline-block mb0">
                                    Will my child be able to build his own website after this course?
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    Yes, each student will be able to build a basic functional website after the course.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="title">
                                <h4 class="inline-block mb0">
                                    Will my child be able to learn languages like C, Java after this course?
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    This course will make it easier for the child to apply logic to computer
                                    programming, and that will go a long way in helping him/her learn new languages.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="title">
                                <h4 class="inline-block mb0">
                                    Will this course be helpful if my child wants to pursue computer engineering later?
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    Yes, with a stronghold on basics as well as good amount of effort, the child will be
                                    able to do well as a computer engineer.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                    </ul>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>
    <section class="bg-white">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row v-align-children">
                <div class="col-sm-5">
                    <h3>Join Coding Blocks and
                        <br> get ahead of the curve.</h3>
                    <p class="lead mb40">
                    </p>
                    <div class="overflow-hidden mb32 mb-xs-24">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-1">
                                <i class="ti-package icon icon-sm pull-left"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-10">
                                <h6 class="uppercase mb0 inline-block p32">Enroll with Code4Kids and get special offer</h6>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="overflow-hidden mb32 mb-xs-24">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-1">
                                <i class="ti-medall-alt icon icon-sm pull-left"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-11">
                                <h6 class="uppercase mb0 inline-block p32">Exciting Prizes and Goodies for all kids</h6>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="pricing-table pt-1 text-center emphasis">
                        <span class="price">â‚¹5,000</span>
                        <p class="lead">(10 Classes)</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-white btn-lg" href="#course-register" disabled="disabled">Coming Soon</a>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>
    <!-- Footer -->
    {{> review-course-section}}
    {{> map}}
    {{> footer}}
</div>
{{> scripts}}
</body>
</html>
